text.tspan: -di : Translation of Ci with respect to C(i-1) along the z axis of Ci
-ai : Translation of Ci with respect to C(i-1) along the x axis of Ci
-αi : Rotation of Ci with respect to C(i-1) around the x axis of Ci
-δi : Rotation of Ci with respect to C(i-1) around the y axis of Ci
-ji: Rotation of C(i+1) around the z axis of C(i+1)
